WEBVTT

00:00:00.446 --> 00:00:02.263
kaset numer dray.

00:00:01.627 --> 00:00:02.786
nu

00:00:02.623 --> 00:00:07.089
un mir hobn oyfgehert vi ir dertseylt vi di amerikaner hobn gegebn guter zakhn.

00:00:05.778 --> 00:00:13.302
yo, zey hobn undz gegebn, un nokh dem zenen zey gekumen, un di meydlekh hobn ongehoybn tsu geyn organizirn, velkhe zey hobn gekent,

00:00:13.302 --> 00:00:15.740
zenen zey gelofn fun eyn vagon in andern,

00:00:15.740 --> 00:00:19.605
ober vifl me hot dokh nebekh nisht getoygt, vayl me iz geven zeyer shvakh.

00:00:19.616 --> 00:00:22.226
nu ikh ho'mir oykh genumen a broyt,

00:00:22.367 --> 00:00:24.066
nisht mer vayl

00:00:24.425 --> 00:00:25.719
ikh hob nisht gekent.

00:00:25.927 --> 00:00:30.461
me hot genumen margarinen, broytn, deys, yents, un zey hobn gemisht un me,

00:00:30.838 --> 00:00:32.522
me hot undz arayngefirt

00:00:32.522 --> 00:00:34.038
keyn

00:00:34.652 --> 00:00:36.250
r- Shartakh,

00:00:37.841 --> 00:00:39.897
noent fun di vagonen.

00:00:39.900 --> 00:00:42.361
arayngefirt un dort ho'mir bakumen

00:00:42.361 --> 00:00:45.432
se geven lere dires, lere sheyne.

00:00:45.435 --> 00:00:48.419
do iz gezesn etlekhe un dort, un me hot,

00:00:48.419 --> 00:00:50.621
di amerikaner hobn gegeben esn,

00:00:50.632 --> 00:00:52.452
se geven aldings.

00:00:52.452 --> 00:00:54.845
un me iz nokh gegangen in kleyt

00:00:55.020 --> 00:00:57.337
fun fun keyn,

00:00:57.337 --> 00:00:59.767
se geven ver se ge- aroysgelofn,

00:00:59.778 --> 00:01:02.506
mentshn hobn zikh ayngeshtelt

00:01:02.647 --> 00:01:06.112
fun deye heftlingen vu ikh bin gevezn,

00:01:06.112 --> 00:01:09.395
zenen gekumen, se hot geven noente pletser

00:01:09.395 --> 00:01:16.997
zenen arayn, zenen arayn in di shtiber un zey hobn a- genumen zakhn, zey hobn zikh ongeton, zey hobn gebrengt stofirn, zey hobn getrofn rendlekh,

00:01:16.997 --> 00:01:21.055
zey hobn getrofn, zey hobn geshmoyst mit di mit di mentshn.

00:01:21.570 --> 00:01:22.790
ikh hob dos nisht getun.

00:01:22.914 --> 00:01:23.904
ikh hobn nisht ge⟨UNK⟩.

00:01:24.112 --> 00:01:25.443
ikh hob gedankt got

00:01:25.443 --> 00:01:29.063
az ikh bin fun dort aroysgegangen, hitstert loz got helfn

00:01:29.063 --> 00:01:30.519
se zol vayter geyn.

00:01:30.035 --> 00:01:31.987
vi lang zent ir dort farblibn?

00:01:32.673 --> 00:01:35.430
fun dort hot men undz arayngefirt keyn Feldafing.

00:01:35.857 --> 00:01:36.898
Feldafing.

00:01:36.414 --> 00:01:38.450
yo. dort bin ikh aheymgekumen,

00:01:37.427 --> 00:01:39.531
dertseylt zhe vos iz geven in Feldafing.

00:01:39.300 --> 00:01:44.140
in Feldafing hot men undz arayngefirt, vu Hitler Yugnt iz geven.

00:01:44.140 --> 00:01:49.672
zeyer a sheyner blok, se geven azoy sheyn az se a UNK vi azoy dort iz geven tsuge-

00:01:49.998 --> 00:01:51.143
nisht poshet.

00:01:51.143 --> 00:01:52.609
nu, ober der

00:01:53.272 --> 00:01:58.953
undzere khevres hobn ales tsebrokhn, durkhgemakht, ongemakht, getun.

00:01:59.111 --> 00:02:00.489
nisht poshet.

00:02:00.596 --> 00:02:02.902
gegesn hot men gegebn.

00:02:02.992 --> 00:02:05.838
me hot gekokht, gut esn.

00:02:06.350 --> 00:02:09.635
mit mir in blok iz gezesn a froy,

00:02:10.299 --> 00:02:13.173
vos der man iz ir aheymgekumen,

00:02:13.218 --> 00:02:15.356
iz er geven a litvanisher.

00:02:15.851 --> 00:02:19.122
un er iz geven in di mener blok,

00:02:19.122 --> 00:02:21.257
un zi iz geven in mayn blok.

00:02:21.285 --> 00:02:23.847
ikh hob gehat mayn bet dos ershte,

00:02:23.847 --> 00:02:25.788
ober azoy vi dey iz gekumen,

00:02:25.788 --> 00:02:29.227
hob ikh gegebn hintn un ikh bin gekrokhn oybn.

00:02:29.385 --> 00:02:31.354
se hot mir azoy gepast.

00:02:31.460 --> 00:02:37.853
nu, er fleg kokhn hindlekh, mit dey, mit yenem, er fleg brengen farn vayb tsu esn,

00:02:37.853 --> 00:02:39.875
ober er hot mikh oykh in zin gehat.

00:02:40.083 --> 00:02:42.963
zi hot gezogt, zi hot zikh getrofn a tokhter.

00:02:43.037 --> 00:02:43.960
oyf mir.

00:02:44.285 --> 00:02:48.814
un er hot mikh lib gehat, un er iz, er iz geven a tsufridn

00:02:48.842 --> 00:02:51.396
vayl az Berta iz nisht aleyn.

00:02:51.396 --> 00:02:56.362
dakht zikh mir ikh ze zi far di oygn, a litvanishe froy, zeyer a inteligente.

00:02:57.110 --> 00:03:02.448
er hot mir gegebn gelt, er hot mir keyn ⟨Munchen⟩, er hot mir gemakht a- di hor,

00:03:02.448 --> 00:03:04.937
az ikh zol shener, az ikh zol zayn azoy.

00:03:04.937 --> 00:03:10.419
un hitster ze ikh vel dir khasene makhn mitn bestn yat fun Liteve.

00:03:11.302 --> 00:03:13.440
du bist mayn kind un.

00:03:13.563 --> 00:03:14.941
ikh hob zey ongekukt,

00:03:15.470 --> 00:03:19.923
ikh hob nisht gezogt yo, ikh hob nisht gezogt neyn. se mir nisht geshtanen in der kop

00:03:19.923 --> 00:03:24.158
oyf dem, ober se iz gut geven tsu hern a gut vort.

00:03:24.158 --> 00:03:26.031
yeder iz mikh mekane geven.

00:03:26.031 --> 00:03:28.419
vayl az me hot gebrengt dos esn in blok,

00:03:28.419 --> 00:03:31.344
hob ikh nisht gebroykht deys tsu esn, vayl ikh hob gehat

00:03:31.400 --> 00:03:33.301
frishe hindl zup,

00:03:34.944 --> 00:03:37.793
er hot gebrengt farn vayb un er hot gebrengt far mir.

00:03:37.793 --> 00:03:41.131
eyn mol hobn zikh deye tsvey, ikh veys nisht vos, tsekrigt,

00:03:41.407 --> 00:03:43.311
un der man iz nisht gekumen,

00:03:43.311 --> 00:03:47.865
un dos vayb hot geveynt. un fregst nisht! un ikh bin geven di meklerin.

00:03:48.157 --> 00:03:50.466
az ikh hob mikh avek gegangen shpatsirn

00:03:50.466 --> 00:03:52.388
in blok fun di mener.

00:03:52.781 --> 00:03:53.934
dort UNK,

00:03:53.934 --> 00:03:56.465
biz ikh hob ofn gepakt un ikh hob im gezen.

00:03:56.465 --> 00:04:01.426
un er iz aroysgekumen, "vos makht ir Regina?" un nokh a mol un a nokh a mol, aher, ahin,

00:04:01.426 --> 00:04:03.794
zog ikh, "vos epes kumt ir nisht tsun undz?

00:04:04.053 --> 00:04:10.089
se mir azoy umheymlekh. az ir zent gekumen, ho'mir gelakht, ho'mir geredt, un Berta vart aykh." un ikh,

00:04:10.449 --> 00:04:12.303
ikh hob gemakht, er hot zikh azoy,

00:04:12.303 --> 00:04:13.990
meynt ikh hob zey nisht far⟨UNK⟩?

00:04:13.990 --> 00:04:18.240
oy! se geven far im az me hot mir geklapt in rukn, Riki, du bist a mentsh!

00:04:19.173 --> 00:04:21.580
vi lang zent ir dort geblin in Feldafing?

00:04:21.114 --> 00:04:24.078
biz september um dritn.

00:04:25.029 --> 00:04:31.301
tsvishn di tsayt, fun dem, fun dem vi ir zent bafrayt gevorn, may finef un fertsik, biz tseptember dray,

00:04:29.670 --> 00:04:30.441
yo

00:04:31.374 --> 00:04:38.405
hot ir getrofn epes bekante? ir hot zikh dervust epes vegn kroyvim? tsi se epes iber- ibergelebt, oder emetser getrofn?

00:04:37.162 --> 00:04:40.129
neyn, neyn, neyn. far dem bin ikh aheymgekumen.

00:04:40.129 --> 00:04:43.850
vayl dafke hobn gemakht di amerikaner, zenen gekumen,

00:04:43.850 --> 00:04:46.458
me hot gemakht a zitsung mit di heftlingen,

00:04:46.458 --> 00:04:49.951
un me hot ongehoybn zogn, "ir zolt azoy, kinder,"

00:04:49.951 --> 00:04:51.281
di amerikaner,

00:04:51.692 --> 00:04:54.032
"ir hot nisht vos tsu geyn aheym,

00:04:54.543 --> 00:05:00.726
vayl ir hot dokh do plakatn, ir zet dokh ver yo un ver nisht un ver se nisht lebt un vi azoy nisht,

00:05:00.726 --> 00:05:03.240
un nor geyn tsvishn dey roybers tsurik,

00:05:03.240 --> 00:05:06.201
ober az ir, az ir vet blaybn do

00:05:06.201 --> 00:05:11.711
fun do hot ir a meglekhkeyt tsu geyn keyn Amerike, un efsher zenen zey oykhet in Amerike."

00:05:11.711 --> 00:05:13.674
zey hobn zayer ayngeredt.

00:05:14.085 --> 00:05:17.761
plutsem nor iz mir ayngefaln, neyn, ikh gey aheym.

00:05:17.761 --> 00:05:19.069
ikh kum aheym.

00:05:19.080 --> 00:05:20.897
ay, ikh hob nisht getrofn?

00:05:21.527 --> 00:05:24.553
ikh hob ober gevust me hot farshtupt in keler,

00:05:24.553 --> 00:05:26.668
vu me hot gevoynt, rendlekh,

00:05:26.775 --> 00:05:28.254
fun mayn bruder

00:05:29.002 --> 00:05:32.771
un se iz aheymgekumen a zun fun deyer mishpokhe,

00:05:32.771 --> 00:05:36.422
vos er hot ⟨zi⟩ nebekh a shtup arayn un er iz shoyn antlofn.

00:05:36.495 --> 00:05:38.227
vayl me hot undz shoyn gefirt.

00:05:38.587 --> 00:05:43.340
hob ikh geklert, nu deys vet dokh dort blaybn, ver veyst tsi der Sruli iz aheymgekumen?

00:05:43.565 --> 00:05:47.334
un un der andere hot dokh nisht gevust, er iz geven in UNK.

00:05:47.334 --> 00:05:50.903
se geven oyf mir a UNK, ikh hob nisht gevust ver vos ven.

00:05:50.903 --> 00:05:52.759
az ikh bin aheymgekumen,

00:05:52.759 --> 00:05:57.037
iz do shoyn geven aroysgenumen, yo, Sruli

00:05:54.635 --> 00:05:56.064
in Siget.

00:05:57.037 --> 00:06:02.392
hot es, az me iz arayngekumen iz geven in der heym tsvey shvester un a bruder,

00:06:02.972 --> 00:06:05.093
un dey hobn nisht gevust fun gornisht.

00:06:05.233 --> 00:06:07.803
un az der Sruli iz arayngekumen in hoyf,

00:06:07.803 --> 00:06:10.731
hot er a vorf arop dos zekl,

00:06:10.731 --> 00:06:17.920
un lebn der tir vu me geyt aroyf tsu der kokh iz geven der keler aroptsugeyn un er iz shoyn arop geshprungen in keler.

00:06:17.923 --> 00:06:20.702
un er iz aroyfgekumen mitn shakhtele,

00:06:20.775 --> 00:06:22.828
mit di rendlekh un mitn gold.

00:06:24.639 --> 00:06:34.956
zenen shteyn geblibn deye. ober vos, zey hobn ongehoybn handlen mit di mit di ungarn, me iz geforn, me iz gegangen, biz ikh bin aheymgekumen, vayl zey zenen gikher gekumen.

00:06:34.967 --> 00:06:36.531
se hot zikh oysgeklibn,

00:06:37.295 --> 00:06:42.183
ir zent gekumen keyn Siget. vemen hot, vos hot ir zikh dervust, un vemen hot ir getrofn in Siget?

00:06:42.003 --> 00:06:43.887
kumendik fun

00:06:44.096 --> 00:06:45.789
funem RAKEVET,

00:06:45.789 --> 00:06:48.882
vu ikh bin ongekumen mit di dray shvester.

00:06:49.091 --> 00:06:53.979
bakumen ho'mir epes a por funt in in Sakmer,

00:06:54.204 --> 00:06:55.425
in Sakmer,

00:06:55.425 --> 00:06:56.392
baym Zhoynt.

00:06:56.702 --> 00:07:01.508
nu, ikh bin ongekumen, ikh ken dokh nisht geyn tsu fus, ikh vey- ikh veys shoyn nisht vu ikh bin,

00:07:01.528 --> 00:07:03.550
hot men genumen a fyaker,

00:07:03.550 --> 00:07:04.678
mit a ferd,

00:07:04.818 --> 00:07:10.081
un mir ho'mir zikh arayngezetst, un mir ze'mir gekumen oyf undzer gas di gantse leng vu me veyst.

00:07:10.081 --> 00:07:12.069
azoy vi ikh kum,

00:07:12.598 --> 00:07:16.237
kumt mir antkegn der geshvesterkind, er geyt oyfn ⟨mertsh⟩.

00:07:16.344 --> 00:07:23.395
un der derzet un tut a vorf mitn bitsikl, "Riki!" hot er ongehoybn shrayen, shoyn.

00:07:23.395 --> 00:07:25.957
bin ikh gegangen tsu zey aheym,

00:07:26.435 --> 00:07:28.592
iz geven tsvey shvester in shtub,

00:07:28.595 --> 00:07:29.951
un dey meydlekh

00:07:29.951 --> 00:07:31.728
zenen gegan tsu got.

00:07:32.291 --> 00:07:33.112
tsu?

00:07:33.489 --> 00:07:35.275
zey hobn nisht gehat vu tsu geyn.

00:07:35.275 --> 00:07:39.536
ikh hob zey geladnt oyf peysekh, ikh hob zey ibergelozt dos shtub, ikh hob zey gegebn, ikh

00:07:39.536 --> 00:07:42.522
nisht UNK. in ale zaytn hob ikh zey gekent helfn.

00:07:42.522 --> 00:07:45.493
un mayn man zol zikh mien, iz er geven zeyer a guter

00:07:45.493 --> 00:07:47.912
az se hot im nisht gehart vos ikh tu.

00:07:48.525 --> 00:07:50.646
ven hot ir getrofn zikh mit ayer man?

00:07:50.718 --> 00:07:53.058
in finef un fertsik.

00:07:53.047 --> 00:07:55.117
bald ven ir zent ongekumen keyn Siget?

00:07:54.549 --> 00:07:56.535
nisht oyf lang.

00:07:57.148 --> 00:07:59.167
ayer man hot geheysn?

00:07:59.186 --> 00:07:59.994
Shimen.

00:08:00.050 --> 00:08:02.474
un vu iz er geven in tsayt fun der milkhome?

00:08:02.632 --> 00:08:05.056
er iz geven in MUNKASZAZOLT.

00:08:04.590 --> 00:08:06.002
un er iz gekumen tsurik.

00:08:05.130 --> 00:08:07.217
e riz gekumen tsurik.

00:08:07.458 --> 00:08:09.393
hot ir zikh getrofn mit im,

00:08:08.370 --> 00:08:09.827
yo, yo.

00:08:09.827 --> 00:08:11.185
er hot gehat a froy,

00:08:11.185 --> 00:08:12.687
ikh hob di froy gekent.

00:08:12.605 --> 00:08:14.186
far di milkhome?

00:08:12.687 --> 00:08:16.784
yo. un un a yingele a sheyns,

00:08:17.398 --> 00:08:20.753
un vos hot, ken men zogn?

00:08:20.753 --> 00:08:21.931
azoy az,

00:08:21.903 --> 00:08:24.665
zayn froy mit di yingele hobn umgekumen?

00:08:25.852 --> 00:08:26.909
in Oush-

00:08:29.345 --> 00:08:32.725
yo, ikh ho- yo, ikh hob khasene gehat, un

00:08:29.798 --> 00:08:30.909
mit Shimenen,

00:08:31.892 --> 00:08:33.658
dort in Siget take?

00:08:32.725 --> 00:08:34.025
in Siget,

00:08:34.025 --> 00:08:35.164
un m-

00:08:34.137 --> 00:08:35.650
ven hot dos geven?

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:37.557
in finef un fertsik, ende.

00:08:37.631 --> 00:08:39.094
ende finef un fertsik.

00:08:38.339 --> 00:08:39.278
yo.

00:08:39.469 --> 00:08:42.867
un in zibn un fertsik hob ikh gehat dos yingele mayns.

00:08:42.828 --> 00:08:44.189
dort in Siget?

00:08:42.867 --> 00:08:46.530
in Siget, dey sheyner yingele dort.

00:08:45.258 --> 00:08:47.733
dos vel'mir ersht shpeter redn vegn di kinder.

00:08:48.684 --> 00:08:54.365
vi bla- vi lang blaybt ir lebn in Siget un mit vos basheftikt ir zikh?

00:08:54.033 --> 00:08:55.718
er iz geven a shnayder.

00:08:55.718 --> 00:08:57.811
un er hot gehat a shtik verk shtub.

00:08:57.811 --> 00:08:59.330
er hot gehat a mashin.

00:08:59.330 --> 00:09:01.639
un UNK zakhn,

00:09:01.914 --> 00:09:05.945
mebl un do dort, me hot es gekont tsamshlepn, se geven genug,

00:09:05.945 --> 00:09:08.628
er hot gevust, er iz gekumen tsaytlekh aheym,

00:09:08.628 --> 00:09:10.889
hot er gekent zikh organizirn.

00:09:10.889 --> 00:09:13.370
er hot organizirt dort far a mishpokhe

00:09:13.370 --> 00:09:15.133
vos zenen geven tshekhishe

00:09:15.133 --> 00:09:21.537
un er hot zey gemakht in hoyf a gast-hoyz. un er hot zey gebrengt tep mit aldings.

00:09:21.573 --> 00:09:25.359
un dort hot er gevoynt, un nokh dem az ikh hob khasene gehat,

00:09:25.359 --> 00:09:27.831
oykh take in dort UNK bin ikh geblibn,

00:09:27.834 --> 00:09:29.583
ikh hob gehat ales.

00:09:29.572 --> 00:09:32.975
vi lang hot ir farblibn in Siget tsu voynen?

00:09:32.559 --> 00:09:35.507
biz se gekumen, biz akht un fertsik.

00:09:35.563 --> 00:09:36.570
biz a-

00:09:35.597 --> 00:09:37.869
akht, biz akht un fuftsik.

00:09:37.706 --> 00:09:40.215
biz akht un fuftsik hot ir gevoynt in Siget?

00:09:40.406 --> 00:09:43.303
unter di rumenisher, komunistisher regirung?

00:09:43.359 --> 00:09:44.957
vi hot zikh gelebt dortn?

00:09:44.675 --> 00:09:45.412
gut.

00:09:45.468 --> 00:09:47.555
me hot aykh nisht getshepet alts yidn?

00:09:47.257 --> 00:09:47.909
m

00:09:48.422 --> 00:09:49.952
di kinder hobn,

00:09:49.012 --> 00:09:50.326
ke- neyn.

00:09:50.326 --> 00:09:51.600
ikh vel aykh zogn.

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:54.019
di kinder. di kinder iz dokh nokh geven yung,

00:09:54.243 --> 00:09:56.839
di di, zey hobn gelernt,

00:09:54.632 --> 00:09:55.892
zey hobn zikh gelernt.

00:09:56.839 --> 00:10:02.974
ober mayn man hot nisht getun azolkhe zakhn az me zol im pakn, se geven mentshn, me hot zey ayngeshpart,

00:10:02.974 --> 00:10:05.058
zey hobn ongehoybn handlen, me hot getun,

00:10:05.058 --> 00:10:08.576
un se geven arayn zogers, se geven, se geven, nu!

00:10:08.576 --> 00:10:11.991
ir veyst UNK, do iz nisht do meynt ir? do iz oykh do.

00:10:12.890 --> 00:10:16.732
hot ir gevoy- gelebt dort biz in nayntsn hundert akht un fuftsik.

00:10:14.763 --> 00:10:18.014
biz tsu kumen, biz ikh bin gekumen aher.

00:10:18.611 --> 00:10:23.027
a minut, di ale yorn az ir hot do gevoynt, do- dort gevoynt, in Siget,

00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:23.094
nu,

00:10:24.028 --> 00:10:29.085
ven hot ir zikh dervust vos iz geshen mit ayer shvester? ir kent mir dertseyln vos iz geshen mit ayer shvester?

00:10:28.483 --> 00:10:31.700
mit mayn shvester? se iz aheymgekumen eyner

00:10:31.908 --> 00:10:33.792
vos, a bakante,

00:10:33.849 --> 00:10:40.728
un ikh bin gelofn tsun ir un ikh hob zi gefregt, efsher efsher veyst zi, zogt zi, vos heyst, zi hot dokh mit mir geshlofn.

00:10:41.021 --> 00:10:45.313
zi iz geven zeyer shtark eydl, vos me hot ir gegebn hot zi tsugenumen.

